<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <style>
      :root {
        --blue-600: #155dfc;
        --neutral-100: #f5f5f5;
        --zinc-950: #09090b;
        --blue-800: #193cb8;
        --blue-400: #51a2ff;
      }

      body {
        display: flex;
        flex-flow: column wrap;
        gap: 1em;
        margin: 0;
        min-height: 100vh;
      }

      .top-container {
        background-color: var(--zinc-950);
        color: var(--neutral-100);
        padding: 1em;
      }

      .main-title {
        font-size: 2rem;
        font-family: "Trebuchet MS", "Lucida Sans Unicode", "Lucida Grande",
          "Lucida Sans", Arial, sans-serif;
        font-weight: 800;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .welcome-text-container {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
      }

      .welcome-text {
        font-size: 1.4rem;
        font-family: "Gill Sans", "Gill Sans MT", Calibri, "Trebuchet MS",
          sans-serif;
        max-width: 50ch;
      }


      a {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        font-family: "Gill Sans", "Gill Sans MT", Calibri, "Trebuchet MS",
          sans-serif;
        font-weight: 700;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 1em 2em;
        margin-top: 2em;
        margin-bottom: 2em;
        background-color: var(--blue-600);
        color: var(--neutral-100);
        border: 1px solid var(--zinc-950);
        border-radius: 5px;
        box-shadow: 1px 1px var(--blue-800);
        align-self: center;
        transition: transform 400ms 400ms ease-in-out;
      }

      a:hover {
        transform: scale(1.05);
        background-color: var(--blue-800);
      }

      a:active {
        background-color: var(--blue-400);
      }
    </style>
    <title>Game Garden</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="top-container">
        <header>
            <h1 class="main-title">Game Garden</h1>
        </header>
        <main class="welcome-text-container">
          <p class="welcome-text">
            Welcome to Game Garden! ðŸŽ®ðŸŒ¿ Discover the world of gaming at your
            fingertips. Our extensive database offers detailed insights into your
            favorite games, including information about developers, publishers, and
            more. Whether you're reminiscing about classics or exploring the latest
            releases, Game Garden is your go-to hub for gaming knowledge.
          </p>
          <p class="welcome-text">
            Start exploring now and let your gaming adventure blossom!
          </p>
        </main>
    </div>

    <a href="./games/all">Start Exploring</a>
  </body>
</html>
